data.description:
This luxurious retreat is nestled adjacent to the Horizon Golf Course. As you step inside, you'll be captivated by the fine details and top-notch features that define this property.

- Hand trowel texture and rounded corners throughout, 8' doors adding an air of grandeur to every room.
Elegance Meets Functionality:
Enjoy the spaciousness of ceramic flooring in the living area, providing both style and durability.
Gather around the 42'' contemporary fireplace for cozy evenings with loved ones.
Luxuriate in a spacious master suite with barn door, his and hers sinks, walk in closet and soaker bath tub.
Granite countertops and beautiful backsplash adds a touch of opulence to the kitchen.
Enjoy the convenience of a reverse osmosis drinking faucet and a whole home water filtration system.
Stackable sliding doors and skylight infuse the home with natural light.
This property offers both elegance and functionality for those that appreciate the finer things in life.
Updated hours and showing availability.
